vaccineGroup.contraindicationText: Do not vaccinate if the patient is pregnant.
Do not vaccinate if the patient has had an adverse reaction to a vaccine component.

vaccineGroup.observationTitle: Severe allergic reaction after previous dose of HPV
vaccineGroup.contraindicationText: Do not vaccinate if the patient has had a severe allergic reaction after a previous dose of HPV vaccine.
Do not vaccinate with 9vHPV if the patient has a hypersensitivity to yeast.
